	   <tr><td colspan=2>Did anyone else notice that when u started using your focus items you started summoning ALOT more green pets??&nbsp;&nbsp;I never summoned green pets prior to obtaining my focus items..and as soon as started using them...GREEN PETS!??!?!  And NO I did not level.  It was odd...all through L35 blue pets...use focus item, many greenies.  Heh, maybe it's just  a coincidence..or I am just messed up.  Dunno.  Anyone else experience this?<br><br>Cheers,<br><br>Beep.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
