	   <tr><td colspan=2>First off, focus items do NOT increase the dmg the pet does.&nbsp;&nbsp;It raises stats.  For example:<br>Fire focus item used gives a fire pet the hp of and air pet.<br>Air focus item used gives an air pet the hp of a water pet.<br>Water focus item used gives a water pet the hp of an earth pet.<br>Earth focux item used gives an earth pet increased stats, such as + agility, + str, + dex..  and so on.  This is what focus items do.  Im not really sure if it makes its spell hit harder, it might.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
